description: This file initializes and renders the React application by creating a root element and rendering the main App component within React.StrictMode.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering React components, targeting the DOM element with ID 'root'.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the root container; in this case, the React.StrictMode wrapping the App component.
